OL,3,CGovernment may restrict jury trials
OL,4,Cfor only the most serious cases
OL,6,FJustice Secretary David Lammy has
OL,7,Freportedly written to officials
OL,8,Fsuggesting that only rape, murder and
OL,9,Fmanslaughter cases might be heard by
OL,10,Fjuries under plans to overhaul the
OL,11,Fcourt system.
OL,13,FLammy wrote in a memo seen by The
OL,14,FTimes newspaper that there was "no
OL,15,Fright" to jury trials in the UK and
OL,16,Fthat the move would not compromise a
OL,17,Fsuspect's rights.
