OL,3,CGovernment may restrict jury trials
OL,4,Cfor only the most serious cases
OL,6,FThe prime minister's official
OL,7,Fspokesman said: "Jury trials will
OL,8,Fremain a cornerstone of our justice
OL,9,Fsystem for the most serious cases.
OL,11,F"No final decisions have been taken,
OL,12,Fbut it is right that we ask whether
OL,13,Fthere are cases that need not be heard
OL,14,Fby a jury."
OL,16,FAsked if Prime Minister Keir Starmer
OL,17,Fwould be comfortable with a situation
OL,18,Fwhere the only cases that went before
OL,19,Fa jury were homicides and rapes, the
OL,20,Fspokesman added: "I think we're
OL,21,Fslightly getting ahead of things.
