OL,6,F"We are looking at the review, no
OL,7,Fdecisions have been taken, and we will
OL,8,Frespond accordingly."
OL,10,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,11,Falso said: "We have been clear there
OL,12,Fis a crisis in the courts, causing
OL,13,Fpain and anguish to victims - with
OL,14,F78,000 cases in the backlog and rising
OL,15,F- which will require bold action to
OL,16,Fput right."
