OL,11,FCommenting on the reports, Law Society
OL,12,Fof England and Wales president Mark
OL,13,FEvans said the "extreme measure" on
OL,14,Fjury trials "goes far beyond"
OL,15,Frecommendations made by Sir Brian.
OL,17,F"This is a fundamental change to how
OL,18,Four criminal justice system operates
OL,19,Fand it goes too far," he said.
