OL,6,FElsewhere, Conservative leader Kemi
OL,7,FBadenoch also criticised the plan,
OL,8,Fdescribing Labour as wanting to "shred
OL,9,Fthis basic right", adding: "It is a
OL,10,Fshort-term decision that risks
OL,11,Ffairness, undermines public trust, and
OL,12,Ferodes the very foundation of our
OL,13,Fjustice system."
OL,15,FLib Dem justice spokeswoman Jess Brown-
OL,16,FFuller also described the reports as
OL,17,F"completely disgraceful" and accused
OL,18,Fministers of dismantling the justice
OL,19,Fsystem and failing victims.
